data.description: Introducing 4058 Draco Drive. A Gorgeous, Recently Updated Home with a Studio!This stunning property offers a spacious and modern living space, perfect for those seeking comfort, style, and versatility. With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this home provides ample space for families or individuals looking for a cozy retreat.But that's not all - 4058 Draco Dr also boasts a finished studio with 1 bathroom, a convenient kitchenette, and a newer roof. This additional space opens up a world of possibilities, making it an ideal short-term rental option for travel nurses or military housing. Imagine the potential for extra income or the opportunity to accommodate guests with ease.Step inside and be greeted by a gorgeous modern color palette that exudes warmth and sophistication. The recent updates to this home have been carefully curated to create a stylish and inviting atmosphere that you'll love coming home to. Plus, enjoy the comfort of a controlled temperature with the included AC unit.Located in the highly sought-after Vandenberg Village community, this home offers the perfect blend of tranquility and convenience. Enjoy a short commute to shopping centers, local eateries, and scenic biking trails, making it an ideal location for those who value both relaxation and accessibility.Don't miss out on the chance to make this house your home just in time for the holidays. Call today to schedule a tour and experience the charm and endless possibilities.
